---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro'
import Notification from '../components/Notification.astro';
---

<Layout title="Brawl Gallery">
	<Notification from="Developer" text="Hi! This page is currently unfinished, but don't worry, we're working hard on it. You can anyway access to the page. Enjoy!" time="Right now" />
	<main>
		<section class="welcome">
			<h1>
				<p style="margin-bottom: -100px; font-size: 60px;">BRAWL</p>
				<p>GALLERY</p>
			</h1>
		</section>
		
		<section class="explanation">
			<p>
				Hi there! You may be asking what is this web page, so here you have the answer. Our objective is to build a place where you can see all brawlers from brawl stars data. You can see the skins of each character, their gadgets, habilities, stellars and more.
			</p>

			<p>
				If you want to support, you can follow me <a href="https://github.com/mpratdev">here</a>. Don't worry, it's completely FREE and it would help me a lot to reach more people!
			</p>

			<p>
				Thank you for your time and hope you enjoy this project!
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="buttons">
			<Button text='GALLERY' href="/gallery" />
			<Button text='SUPPORT' href="/support" />
		</section>

		<section class="explanation" style="margin-top: 25px;">
			<p>
				If you keep reading, let me explain you who am I. My name is Mart√≠ and I'm a programer who does lots of diferent projects.
			</p>

			<p>
				Although I have some experience on this, I know I always can improve my projects, so please, if you have any recomendation or suposition, I would really appreciate if you write me an e-mail and tell me whatever you want. You can do it by clicking on the next button:
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="buttons mail">
			<Button text='mpratmaya@gmail.com' href="mailto:mpratmaya@gmail.com" color="mail"/>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		height: 1060px;
	}

	h1 p {
        font-size: 80px;
        text-shadow: 10px 10px 0px black;
        color: red;
    }

    h1 {
        margin: auto;
    }

	main {
		width: 100%;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.explanation {
		margin-top: -40px;
	}

	.explanation p {
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 21px;
	}

	.explanation a {
		color: #f00;
	}

	.buttons {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		margin-top: 55px;
	}

	.mail {
		margin-top: 15px;
	}
</style>
